{"type":"message","id":"fec414f9","parentId":"7064c49e","timestamp":"2026-04-15T13:30:06.009Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 能解决，这个报错本质上是：\n\n**当前会话上下文太长，压缩时预留 token 太少，导致还没来得及稳定 compaction 就被重置了。**\n\n你这个提示里已经给了最直接的修法：\n\n## 直接修法\n\n编辑你的 OpenClaw 配置文件：\n\n`/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n\n把这里：\n\n```json\n\"agents\": {\n  \"defaults\": {\n    \"compaction\": {\n      \"mode\": \"safeguard\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n改成：\n\n```json\n\"agents\": {\n  \"defaults\": {\n    \"compaction\": {\n      \"mode\": \"safeguard\",\n      \"reserveTokensFloor\": 20000\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n如果你经常长对话，我建议直接用：\n\n```json\n\"reserveTokensFloor\": 30000\n```\n\n## 为什么有用\n\n`reserveTokensFloor` 是给 compaction 留的安全余量。  \n太小的话，长会话到了边缘就容易出现：\n\n- 还没压缩完就超上下文\n- 压缩后重试空间不够\n- 最终被系统 reset fresh\n\n## 改完之后\n\n通常还需要让 Gateway 重新加载配置，最稳的是重启一次：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n## 我对你这套环境的建议\n\n你现在主打：\n- heartbeat\n- clawCast 学习\n- 多 Agent 编排\n- 长会话持续运行\n\n所以我建议至少这样配：\n\n```json\n\"compaction\": {\n  \"mode\": \"safeguard\",\n  \"reserveTokensFloor\": 30000\n}\n```\n\n这样更稳一点。\n\n如果你愿意，我可以直接帮你把配置改掉，并顺手检查一下 JSON 是否正确。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_02913e840dfafe750169df92d628588193bf698d8132244819\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":2552,"output":419,"cacheRead":34432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37403,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776259795916,"responseId":"resp_02913e840dfafe750169df92d5342081939735dc8b43b15845"}}
