{"type":"message","id":"be771628","parentId":"177aae7b","timestamp":"2026-04-15T13:31:24.778Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好，我已经帮你改了。\n\n已更新：\n`/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n\n现在是：\n\n```json\n\"compaction\": {\n  \"mode\": \"safeguard\",\n  \"reserveTokensFloor\": 30000\n}\n```\n\n我也顺手校验了 JSON，格式没问题。\n\n下一步你执行一下：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n重启后新配置才会生效。\n\n补一句，你刚才那条 `Exec failed ... SIGTERM` 不是这次改配置失败，而是我之前跑 `openclaw status` 时被环境侧中断了，不影响这次配置修改。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_068f2a4fbe1d55890169df93298af48190b8f729ff239c541c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":37934,"output":163,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38097,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776259879008,"responseId":"resp_068f2a4fbe1d55890169df93283b508190ac696550332869ef"}}
