{"type":"message","id":"6764a4ed","parentId":"a7429f76","timestamp":"2026-04-15T13:32:40.122Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_tXhJjZCLoqji42fbjSbZSEVt|fc_098e8dead48565e30169df93703d4081959234d49b2749631d","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Gateway service disabled.\nStart with: openclaw gateway install\nStart with: openclaw gateway\nStart with: systemctl --user start openclaw-gateway.service\nStart with: systemd user services are unavailable; install/enable systemd or run the gateway under your supervisor.\nStart with: If you're in a container, run the gateway in the foreground instead of `openclaw gateway`."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6709,"aggregated":"Gateway service disabled.\nStart with: openclaw gateway install\nStart with: openclaw gateway\nStart with: systemctl --user start openclaw-gateway.service\nStart with: systemd user services are unavailable; install/enable systemd or run the gateway under your supervisor.\nStart with: If you're in a container, run the gateway in the foreground instead of `openclaw gateway`.","cwd":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776259960119}}
{"type":"message","id":"52c3a522","parentId":"6764a4ed","timestamp":"2026-04-15T13:32:48.086Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 重启命令执行了，但结果是：\n\n**你的 Gateway 不是 systemd 服务模式，所以 `openclaw gateway restart` 不能直接用。**\n\n返回的是：\n- `Gateway service disabled`\n- 当前更像是前台运行 / 容器运行 / 非 systemd user service 环境\n\n你现在有 2 个可行方案。\n\n## 推荐方案\n\n直接启动前台 Gateway：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway\n```\n\n如果你本来就是这样跑 OpenClaw，这样最对路。\n\n## 另一种方案\n\n如果你想以后能用 `restart` 这种命令，就先安装 service：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway install\n```\n\n但前提是这台机器支持 user-level systemd。  \n从返回信息看，**你当前环境大概率不支持**，所以这条不一定能走通。\n\n## 结论\n\n你现在最该做的是直接运行：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway\n```\n\n如果你愿意，我可以继续帮你：\n1. 先检查当前 Gateway 现在是不是已经有别的方式在跑\n2. 如果没跑，再给你最稳的启动方式\n\n你回我一句 **“继续查”**，我就直接接着做。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_064fd0fdec0188c10169df937ac2a081948671418306d423c3\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":38308,"output":276,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38584,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776259960125,"responseId":"resp_064fd0fdec0188c10169df9379520881949e84e9888f0b12c7"}}
