{"type":"message","id":"5fc39127","parentId":"3a08aa00","timestamp":"2026-04-15T13:40:24.624Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 可以，主控 Agent 这边你直接用下面任一方式都行。\n\n## 最简单\n\n在当前对话里发送：\n\n```text\n/new\n```\n\n这会给**当前主控会话**开一个新会话。\n\n## 如果你是想“保留旧会话，但另起一个新的主控入口”\n\n那要看你现在是通过哪个入口接入主控的。对微信直连这种场景，通常 `/new` 就是对的。\n\n## 说明\n\n你前面那个“context limit exceeded”本质上也是会话过长，  \n所以现在手动 `/new` 很合适，能马上把上下文切干净。\n\n如果你愿意，我也可以顺手告诉你：\n\n- `/new`\n- `/compact`\n- 调高 `reserveTokensFloor`\n\n这三个分别适合什么场景。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0583289714e4381d0169df9544dc588195976c10e0b31ce6aa\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":38657,"output":193,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38850,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776260418371,"responseId":"resp_0583289714e4381d0169df9543bb8c8195836420861cd4ec2c"}}
