{"type":"message","id":"a55ece92","parentId":"2b122d72","timestamp":"2026-04-15T13:41:31.201Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 我不能直接代你发送 `/new` 到这条当前聊天控制面里，所以没法替你“按钮式”切过去。\n\n你这边只要发一条：\n\n```text\n/new\n```\n\n就会给**主控 Agent 的当前会话**切到新会话。\n\n如果你愿意，我可以在你发完 `/new` 后，立刻帮你做一件事：\n- 帮你整理新会话开场 prompt\n- 或直接接着你刚才的任务继续，不带旧上下文包袱\n\n你发完 `/new` 后，把新会话第一句话发我就行。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09906e5fe561ab3b0169df95881e608193bb543005a078eb27\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":38925,"output":146,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39071,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776260482937,"responseId":"resp_09906e5fe561ab3b0169df95843cb0819391414d6aa80a4f7f"}}
